  "body": "For example, instead of https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/master/contracts/token/ERC1155/ERC1155.sol#L85\r\n\r\nimplement the loop like this\r\n\r\n```\r\n for (uint256 i = 0; i < accounts.length;) {\r\n            batchBalances[i] = balanceOf(accounts.unsafeMemoryAccess(i), ids.unsafeMemoryAccess(i));\r\n            unchecked {\r\n               ++i;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nBecause the array length cannot exceed uint256, we don't need to check for overflow.",
